article.description: Utah Valley St. 84, Haskell Indian Nations 49
article.headline: Utah Valley St. 84, Haskell Indian Nations 49
article.linkText: Utah Valley St. 84, Haskell Indian Nations 49
article.story: OREM, Utah -- Alfonzo Hubbard had 14 points to lead six Utah Valley players in double figures in an 84-49 victory against Haskell Indian Nations on Friday night. Ben Aird added 13 points, Geddes Robinson and Isiah Williams 12 each, Keawe Enos 11 and Keith Thompson 10 for the Wolverines (5-4). Byron Trujillo scored 17 points for Haskell, a NAIA school in Lawrence, Kan., that classified the game as an exhibition. The Indians' record remained 6-5. Utah Valley shot 18 for 33 (54.5 percent) from the floor in the first half and led 45-16 at intermission.
